message.body: We might want to wait til Alex is done, its really loud. Can you do later on?
Yeah. I'm gonna go for a ride in that case
Cool. Let me know when youre back
15 -30 min? I'm at mt moriah headed your way
More like an hour. Theyre still at it. Me and liz at about to do another run to the cemetary for chips
Hey. What do you think the deal is?
Im having Kyle grab me a set of short reach levers from Fairmont today
Shit. Ok, let me know if he gets them. I ordered some from amazon since all the bike shops were closed today. I can send them back if I need to though
Ok should have them by tuesday
